----
2:1. In the Name of Allah Most Merciful and Compassionate:
ALIF LAM MIM
----
2:2. This, no less, is the Sacred Book:
No doubt is in it;
A mighty guidance for the godfearing;
----
2:3. Who believe in the unseen, keep well the prayer,
and of what We have provided them ever expend.
----
2:4. And who believe in all that has been sent down to you, and was ever sent down before you, and of the afterlife are completely certain.
----
2:5. Those are upon tremendous guidance from their Lord and those are the successful forever.
